  <brief_title>Single Incision Laparoscopic Surgery (SILS) Versus Conventional Laparoscopic Hysterectomy</brief_title>
  <official_title>Multi-institution, Randomized Trial for Efficacy and Safety of Single Incision Laparoscopic Surgery (SILS) Versus Conventional Laparoscopic Hysterectomy for the Treatment of Uterine Myoma or Adenomyosis</official_title>
  <sponsors>
