  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Multi-center prospective randomized trial of single port laparoscopic surgery (SILS) versus
      conventional 3-4 ports laparoscopic hysterectomy. Hypothesis is that conversion rate of SILS
      is not inferior to that of conventional approach.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
